---------------------------------------------------------------------
Classics for Meditation is a collection of great works that have been selected 
for their easy tempos and smooth flowing melodies. Simply put on the CD and 
block out the outside world to allow focus and total concentration without 
distraction. This collection is perfect for use in healing therapy sessions or 
purely for periods of stress-free relaxation.
